{"tid":425280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人仲記得香港仲有間冇乜人知嘅大學","createTime":"2017-10-05T14:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T15:20:02.000Z","uid":90802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"955f411204831c730d5d56c94922cefeecf902e2","tid":425280,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"香港三育書院 <br />\n雖然係得4個degree course <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.prntscr.com/image/t0kblLaNRcG-RURGrid6jg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.prntscr.com%2Fimage%2Ft0kblLaNRcG-RURGrid6jg.png&h=8c7d7e96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07823b74b2d943148ad98c678fd611378f6b974b","tid":425280,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"香港三育書院於1903年在中國廣州同慶坊（位於今北京路）創辦，初時稱為伯特利女校（The Bethel Girls' School），約於1905年增設益智男校（Yick Chi Boys' School），5年後易名為三育學校（Sam Yuk School）。<br />\n1915至1917年間，兩校先後遷往東山西牛尾，1922年兩校合併為一所稱為三育中學的男女校，一度於1927年改稱神道訓練院，部分學生遷往香港九龍菴由街（今福華街），開設華安學校，成為三育中學第一分校，於翌年遷回廣州。其後又於1935年改稱廣州三育研究社（Canton Training Institute）。<br />\n於1937年，日本侵華，學校遷至香港沙田陳樓，改稱華南三育研究社（South China Training Institute）。翌年，位於南京橋頭鎮之中華三育研究社（China Training Institute）也因戰事決定到香港復校，於1938年與華南三育研究社在沙田合併，更名中華華南三育研究社（China and South China Training Institute），但在香港註冊時仍稱華南三育研究社。其後，學校獲香港政府批准以私產方式出售西貢清水灣道共1,374萬平方呎作為永久校址，首期建築於1939年完成，遷入新址後仍繼續與中華三育研究院合辦。<br />\n太平洋戰爭於1941年爆發，學校又遷回廣東省老隆繼續校務，戰時仍然進行及發展教育工作。戰後由於香港的校舍仍然被英軍借用，未能即時遷回香港，臨時遷回廣州東山三育路，將「三育衛生食品廠」的建築物改建為臨時校舍，直至1947年才返回香港清水灣復校。戰後復校初期，仍然稱為「華南三育研究社」，但在1952至1953年間，再次更名三育中學（Sam Yuk Middle School）。<br />\n1962年，藉大專部成立將校名改為華南三育書院（South China Union College），附設中學部，隨後獲政府批准註冊成一所大專院校。<br />\n1981年秋，正式定名為香港三育書院。"},{"pid":"c9858f160d6d3da0a10e5673fd7e5301da51b2dc","tid":425280,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"著名校友<br />\n<br />\n區瑞強：香港民歌歌手<br />\n王傑：香港流行歌手、音樂人<br />\n殷寧（金慧英）：前亞洲小姐、主持人"},{"pid":"52992658fb1010bb4b944bf5a44f4a76e5efd4e0","tid":425280,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:54:13.000Z","msg":"聽過以為中學嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5343331828d7bd8290f2313bd434a248d73364c","tid":425280,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽過以為中學嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>有預科課程"},{"pid":"1a0eca6dd36f811179bdf354bf1e295358400e14","tid":425280,"uid":66055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"第二個option好似幾正"},{"pid":"7107b3fc38a4642435a036d0315982c66e2ec2f7","tid":425280,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkac.edu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkac.edu&d=IbKkGM7vAtr1qWKz%2FZPBodtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fcecf264\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkac.edu</a><br />\n<br />\n校網讕高級 得英文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1693e449c20b693f4abcf4bbbf41083e94ac8ed","tid":425280,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.panoramio.com/photos/original/8305511.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.panoramio.com%2Fphotos%2Foriginal%2F8305511.jpg&h=ec14a783&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f20091ca3335d8bcdbdc3ec9fd5028629a84fb7","tid":425280,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"大學定大專<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7457c9e1252f30589431c294dfab43e0d06c60c8","tid":425280,"uid":52252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:20:02.000Z","msg":"反而想知呢間有無人讀<br />\n華夏書院<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.huaxia.edu.hk/%E4%B8%BB%E9%A0%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.huaxia.edu.hk%2F%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25A0%2581%2F&d=IbKkGM7vAtr1qWKz%2FZPBodtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5b5e2318\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.huaxia.edu.hk/%E4%B8%BB%E9%A0%81/</a>"}]}